table.name: ENROLLMENT
table.Comment: Information for a student registered for a particular section (class).

table.name: GRADE
table.Comment: The individual grades a student received for a particular section(class).

table.name: GRADE_CONVERSION
table.Comment: Converts a number grade to a letter grade.

table.name: GRADE_TYPE
table.Comment: Lookup table of a grade types (code) and its description.

table.name: GRADE_TYPE_WEIGHT
table.Comment: Information on how the final grade for a particular section is computed. For example, the midterm constitutes 50%, the quiz 10% and the final examination 40% of the final grade.

table.name: SECTION
table.Comment: Information for an individual section (class) of a particular course.

table.name: ZIPCODE
table.Comment: City, state and zip code information.

column.name: COURSE_NO
column.Comment: The unique ID for a course.

column.name: DESCRIPTION
column.Comment: The full name for this course.

column.name: COST
column.Comment: The dollar amount charged for enrollment in this course.

column.name: PREREQUISITE
column.Comment: The ID number of the course which must be taken as a prerequisite to this course.
